videos.description: Justin Crawford's 5-yard touchdown run puts West Virginia on the board.
videos.headline: Crawford powers his way into the end zone

videos.description: Will Grier's seven-yard TD pass to Ka'Raun  White gives the Mountaineers a 14-3 lead.
videos.headline: Grier throws his first TD pass of the game

videos.description: David Sills 40-yard catch puts West Virginia in the red zone.
videos.headline: Grier finds Sills for a huge pick up

videos.description: Kennedy McKoy's 13-yard touchdown  extends the Mountaineers' lead to 21-3.
videos.headline: McKoy's TD run extends West Virginia's lead

videos.description: Will Grier finds an open Marcus Simms for a 52-yard touchdown pass in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Simms outruns coverage for big TD catch

videos.description: Kyzir White intercepts Thomas Sirk for the first turnover of the game.
videos.headline: White intercepts Thomas, puts West Virginia in good field position

videos.description: Will Grier completes a nine-yard touchdown pass to David Sills to extend West Virginia's lead.
videos.headline: Sills beats one-on-one coverage for TD

videos.description: Justin Crawford runs for a 41-yard touchdown late in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Crawford's big run leads to West Virginia TD

videos.description: Will Grier connects with David Sills for a 75-yard touchdown pass in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Grier finds Sills again for another TD

videos.description: Thomas Sirk's 19-yard touchdown pass to Jimmy Williams gives East Carolina its first touchdown of the game.
videos.headline: Sirk passes for first ECU touchdown of the game

videos.description: Will Grier finds David Sills for a four-yard touchdown. It's Grier's fifth touchdown pass of the game and Sills' third touchdown catch.
videos.headline: Grier's fifth TD pass of the game adds to West Virginia's lead
